why did she have another seizure?

598
00:21:57,640 --> 00:21:59,000
Could it be related

599
00:21:59,000 --> 00:21:59,720
to her heart condition?

600
00:22:00,680 --> 00:22:02,240
Based on the current test results,

601
00:22:02,599 --> 00:22:03,480
we can basically rule out

602
00:22:03,519 --> 00:22:04,240
a cardiac cause

603
00:22:04,279 --> 00:22:05,200
for the convulsions.

604
00:22:06,160 --> 00:22:07,240
Her ECG is normal.

605
00:22:07,759 --> 00:22:08,359
The head CT

606
00:22:08,400 --> 00:22:09,119
shows no bleeding

607
00:22:09,119 --> 00:22:09,920
or infarction.

608
00:22:10,240 --> 00:22:11,079
Her blood glucose and electrolytes

609
00:22:11,079 --> 00:22:11,839
are also normal.

610
00:22:12,839 --> 00:22:13,400
So

611
00:22:13,519 --> 00:22:14,480
the more likely cause

612
00:22:14,599 --> 00:22:15,880
is neurological.

613
00:22:17,519 --> 00:22:18,839
Has this happened before?

614
00:22:23,599 --> 00:22:24,519
You can't hide

615
00:22:24,519 --> 00:22:25,359
important information from doctors.

616
00:22:26,680 --> 00:22:27,920
Haven't you already ruled out

617
00:22:28,000 --> 00:22:29,200
a cardiac cause?

618
00:22:30,079 --> 00:22:31,599
Epilepsy can't be cured anyway.

619
00:22:31,920 --> 00:22:32,960
Just fix

620
00:22:32,960 --> 00:22:33,720
my heart problem.

621
00:22:34,440 --> 00:22:35,519
That's not how it works.

622
00:22:36,160 --> 00:22:37,440
Epilepsy can be primary

623
00:22:37,440 --> 00:22:38,319
or secondary.

624
00:22:38,599 --> 00:22:39,720
Your myocardial infarction

625
00:22:39,720 --> 00:22:40,640
and seizure symptoms

626
00:22:40,839 --> 00:22:41,400
may come from

627
00:22:41,400 --> 00:22:42,440
two different systems,

628
00:22:42,720 --> 00:22:43,920
or they may have been triggered

629
00:22:43,920 --> 00:22:44,599
by the same underlying cause.

630
00:22:45,519 --> 00:22:46,759
I recommend consultations

631
00:22:46,759 --> 00:22:48,039
from Neurology and Infectious Diseases.

632
00:22:50,680 --> 00:22:51,759
More consultations?

633
00:22:52,200 --> 00:22:53,720
I've already been here for days.

634
00:22:54,079 --> 00:22:55,119
It never ends.

635
00:22:55,759 --> 00:22:57,039
It's better to investigate properly.

636
00:22:58,559 --> 00:22:59,319
If we can't identify

637
00:22:59,319 --> 00:23:00,200
the cause of the seizures,

638
00:23:00,680 --> 00:23:01,680
your heart problem

639
00:23:01,799 --> 00:23:02,920
could recur too.

640
00:23:05,400 --> 00:23:06,720
Fine. Check it.

641
00:23:08,359 --> 00:23:08,960
Thank you.

642
00:23:10,359 --> 00:23:11,279
Thank you, doctor.

643
00:23:15,559 --> 00:23:16,440
Dr. Zhang,

644
00:23:17,480 --> 00:23:18,200
why is she

645
00:23:18,240 --> 00:23:19,279
covered up so completely?

646
00:23:19,559 --> 00:23:20,759
She looks like a celebrity.

647
00:23:21,839 --> 00:23:23,480
I heard she's

648
00:23:23,519 --> 00:23:24,839
an influencer with over a million followers.

649
00:23:25,200 --> 00:23:26,599
She was admitted with a heart attack days ago.

650
00:23:26,680 --> 00:23:27,640
She's only thirty-six,

651
00:23:28,119 --> 00:23:29,440
and already has triple-vessel disease.

652
00:23:29,880 --> 00:23:31,000
Triple-vessel disease

653
00:23:31,039 --> 00:23:31,960
in such a young woman?

654
00:23:32,599 --> 00:23:33,440
That's rare.

655
00:23:33,759 --> 00:23:34,160
Yes.

656
00:23:35,079 --> 00:23:36,079
And the location

657
00:23:36,119 --> 00:23:36,720
of her infarction was unusual.

658
00:23:37,200 --> 00:23:37,519
During the emergency

659
00:23:37,519 --> 00:23:38,119
PCI,

660
00:23:38,119 --> 00:23:38,960
they only opened

661
00:23:38,960 --> 00:23:39,759
the most severely narrowed vessel.

662
00:23:41,200 --> 00:23:42,640
Her heart problem isn't fully resolved,

663
00:23:42,880 --> 00:23:44,200
and now there's the seizure issue.

664
00:24:06,240 --> 00:24:06,960
What are you doing? Let me...

665
00:24:07,400 --> 00:24:08,079
I came to apologize.

666
00:24:08,599 --> 00:24:10,359
I'm really sorry.

667
00:24:10,799 --> 00:24:12,440
I was the one who secretly filmed you.

668
00:24:12,759 --> 00:24:13,319
Sorry.

669
00:24:13,400 --> 00:24:14,119
I brought you a gift.

670
00:24:14,160 --> 00:24:14,720
It's okay.

671
00:24:14,720 --> 00:24:16,200
As long as you deleted it.

672
00:24:16,480 --> 00:24:16,880
I did.

673
00:24:17,279 --> 00:24:17,920
Here, my phone.

674
00:24:17,920 --> 00:24:18,640
You can check.

675
00:24:18,720 --> 00:24:19,680
All right. I know.

676
00:24:20,279 --> 00:24:21,079
Take these.

677
00:24:21,079 --> 00:24:22,160
They're very sweet.

678
00:24:22,279 --> 00:24:23,160
No, thank you.

679
00:24:23,240 --> 00:24:24,119
Thank you.

680
00:24:24,319 --> 00:24:24,839
Let me see.

681
00:24:25,039 --> 00:24:25,839
Long Jiaojiao.

682
00:24:27,440 --> 00:24:28,160
Long Quan.

683
00:24:29,759 --> 00:24:30,839
I'm Xiao'e.

684
00:24:31,880 --> 00:24:33,119
It is you. Let me look.

685
00:24:33,839 --> 00:24:34,920
It really is you.

686
00:24:35,839 --> 00:24:37,240
Did you get double-eyelid surgery?

687
00:24:37,680 --> 00:24:38,359
Back in school,

688
00:24:38,359 --> 00:24:39,359
you weren't as pretty as me.

689
00:24:39,400 --> 00:24:40,799
How did you get so beautiful?

690
00:24:40,920 --> 00:24:42,119
I'm Xiao'e.

691
00:24:42,440 --> 00:24:43,960
I know. I recognized your voice.

692
00:24:45,720 --> 00:24:46,640
With that loud voice,

693
00:24:46,720 --> 00:24:47,960
I'd know you with my eyes closed.

694
00:24:48,319 --> 00:24:49,160
You recognized me,

695
00:24:49,160 --> 00:24:50,359
but didn't say hello?

696
00:24:50,599 --> 00:24:51,839
How many years has it been?

697
00:24:52,000 --> 00:24:53,400
We haven't seen each other since high school.

698
00:24:54,119 --> 00:24:55,359
Did you miss me?

699
00:24:55,680 --> 00:24:57,200
Don't get so worked up.

700
00:24:57,559 --> 00:24:58,480
How could I not?

701
00:24:58,480 --> 00:24:59,720
I've missed you so much.

702
00:24:59,759 --> 00:25:00,400
Quan.

703
00:25:00,640 --> 00:25:01,039
It really is you.

704
00:25:01,039 --> 00:25:01,839
Zhang Diao'e.

705
00:25:02,079 --> 00:25:02,720
Zhang Diao'e.

706
00:25:03,200 --> 00:25:04,119
I've been looking everywhere for you.

707
00:25:04,279 --> 00:25:04,720
Why did you run off

708
00:25:04,759 --> 00:25:05,759
into someone else's ward again?

709
00:25:06,119 --> 00:25:06,960
She's not someone else.

710
00:25:06,960 --> 00:25:08,079
She's an old classmate.

711
00:25:08,240 --> 00:25:09,720
Your roommate complained about you.

712
00:25:10,039 --> 00:25:10,920
She said you talk too much

713
00:25:11,039 --> 00:25:12,079
and keep her from resting.

714
00:25:12,400 --> 00:25:13,279
Do I talk too much?

715
00:25:14,079 --> 00:25:15,119
Why else would she ask

716
00:25:15,119 --> 00:25:16,000
to change rooms?

717
00:25:16,519 --> 00:25:17,359
She doesn't need to move.

718
00:25:18,200 --> 00:25:18,720
I'll move.

719
00:25:19,240 --> 00:25:20,039
Isn't this bed empty?

720
00:25:20,279 --> 00:25:21,119
I'll move in here.

721
00:25:21,240 --> 00:25:21,839
It's not empty.

722
00:25:21,839 --> 00:25:23,599
A new patient is coming soon.

723
00:25:23,839 --> 00:25:25,680
Let her move into my bed.

724
00:25:26,119 --> 00:25:27,480
I'll stay here with my old classmate.

725
00:25:27,720 --> 00:25:28,319
Look.

726
00:25:28,759 --> 00:25:30,400
We're very close.

727
00:25:30,680 --> 00:25:31,839
We're best friends.

728
00:25:32,759 --> 00:25:34,440
Why are your hands so cold, Quan?

729
00:25:34,680 --> 00:25:35,960
I'll move here and keep you company.

730
00:25:36,000 --> 00:25:36,400
Okay?

731
00:25:39,039 --> 00:25:39,640
I don't mind.

732
00:25:39,799 --> 00:25:40,519
See?

733
00:25:41,160 --> 00:25:41,680
All right.

734
00:25:41,799 --> 00:25:42,799
You don't need to worry about it.

735
00:25:43,200 --> 00:25:44,519
Go back to work.

736
00:25:44,559 --> 00:25:45,839
Then come back soon and pack.

737
00:25:45,880 --> 00:25:46,640
Don't worry.

738
00:25:47,599 --> 00:25:48,039
Quan,

739
00:25:48,039 --> 00:25:49,559
isn't this fate?

740
00:25:49,839 --> 00:25:50,559
Of all places,

741
00:25:50,640 --> 00:25:52,039
we ran into each other in a hospital.

742
00:25:52,680 --> 00:25:53,799
Weren't you called Long Quan?

743
00:25:53,799 --> 00:25:55,720
Why are you Long Jiaojiao now?

744
00:25:56,480 --> 00:25:57,279
I changed it.

745
00:25:57,359 --> 00:25:58,359
Why?

746
00:25:59,319 --> 00:26:00,119
I'll tell you later.

747
00:26:00,880 --> 00:26:01,960
We have plenty of time.

748
00:26:02,839 --> 00:26:03,640
I'm so excited.

749
00:26:04,279 --> 00:26:05,160
I'll come over

750
00:26:05,200 --> 00:26:06,119
and save myself a spot.

751
00:26:06,599 --> 00:26:07,559
Wait for me.

752
00:26:08,680 --> 00:26:10,119
It really is.

753
00:26:10,400 --> 00:26:12,240
See? I told you she's an old classmate.

754
00:26:20,359 --> 00:26:22,079
This Long Jiaojiao case is bizarre.

755
00:26:22,519 --> 00:26:23,720
All her infection markers are negative.

756
00:26:23,759 --> 00:26:24,559
She doesn't have a fever.

757
00:26:25,400 --> 00:26:26,799
Her pathological reflexes and meningeal signs

758
00:26:26,839 --> 00:26:27,519
are also negative.

759
00:26:27,839 --> 00:26:28,319
That doesn't support

760
00:26:28,319 --> 00:26:29,599
a central nervous system infection.

761
00:26:31,000 --> 00:26:31,920
What about the brain MRI?

762
00:26:32,480 --> 00:26:33,119
It showed

763
00:26:33,240 --> 00:26:34,680
scattered punctate white-matter hyperintensities.

764
00:26:36,079 --> 00:26:37,400
But that's nonspecific too.

765
00:26:37,400 --> 00:26:38,559
It doesn't explain much.

766
00:26:39,119 --> 00:26:40,119
If she has been strictly

767
00:26:40,160 --> 00:26:41,160
following medical advice

768
00:26:41,519 --> 00:26:43,000
and taking her medication regularly,

769
00:26:43,000 --> 00:26:44,480
yet the seizures keep recurring,

770
00:26:44,559 --> 00:26:45,400
then something

771
00:26:45,400 --> 00:26:46,240
is definitely off.

772
00:26:49,799 --> 00:26:50,960
Did Neurology recommend a lumbar puncture?

773
00:26:51,680 --> 00:26:52,400
Yes.

774
00:26:52,640 --> 00:26:54,039
But the patient refused.

775
00:26:55,480 --> 00:26:56,359
I'll speak with her.

776
00:26:57,279 --> 00:26:57,880
I'll go too.

777
00:26:59,759 --> 00:27:00,599
Why are you coming?

778
00:27:03,640 --> 00:27:04,359
Director,

779
00:27:04,759 --> 00:27:05,400
I just think

780
00:27:05,400 --> 00:27:06,599
these recurrent seizures

781
00:27:06,599 --> 00:27:07,640
are strange.

782
00:27:08,279 --> 00:27:08,920
What's strange?

783
00:27:10,640 --> 00:27:11,440
Nothing stranger than you.

784
00:27:14,039 --> 00:27:14,519
Yes.

785
00:27:17,400 --> 00:27:18,960
Since I was admitted,

786
00:27:19,640 --> 00:27:20,599
you've drawn tube after tube

787
00:27:20,599 --> 00:27:21,720
of blood

788
00:27:22,240 --> 00:27:23,640
and run test after test.

789
00:27:23,839 --> 00:27:24,200
And still

790
00:27:24,200 --> 00:27:25,359
you haven't found anything.

791
00:27:26,839 --> 00:27:28,000
Am I your lab rat?

792
00:27:28,440 --> 00:27:29,920
Your condition is indeed unusual,

793
00:27:30,359 --> 00:27:30,960
so we need to

794
00:27:30,960 --> 00:27:31,960
rule things out step by step.

795
00:27:33,000 --> 00:27:34,799
I heard you want a lumbar puncture.

796
00:27:35,960 --> 00:27:37,440
That's dangerous.

797
00:27:37,599 --> 00:27:39,240
What if it paralyzes me?

798
00:27:39,640 --> 00:27:40,920
You don't need to worry too much.

799
00:27:41,160 --> 00:27:41,920
A lumbar puncture

800
00:27:41,920 --> 00:27:42,839
is a routine test now.

801
00:27:42,960 --> 00:27:43,799
The chance of that happening

802
00:27:43,799 --> 00:27:44,359
is extremely low.

803
00:27:45,279 --> 00:27:46,799
Why don't you just order

804
00:27:46,799 --> 00:27:47,680
every possible test

805
00:27:47,680 --> 00:27:48,880
all at once?

806
00:27:49,000 --> 00:27:50,079
Today it's one department,

807
00:27:50,079 --> 00:27:51,119
tomorrow another.

808
00:27:51,200 --> 00:27:51,960
Isn't that exhausting?

809
00:27:52,039 --> 00:27:52,519
Just

810
00:27:52,599 --> 00:27:53,920
check everything from head to toe.

811
00:27:54,039 --> 00:27:54,559
It'd be easier.

812
00:27:55,480 --> 00:27:56,799
We can only order tests

813
00:27:56,839 --> 00:27:57,799
when they're medically indicated.

814
00:28:03,279 --> 00:28:03,759
Jiaojiao,

815
00:28:04,279 --> 00:28:05,799
we understand

816
00:28:06,200 --> 00:28:07,000
that you're unwell

817
00:28:07,039 --> 00:28:08,119
and your mother is worried.

818
00:28:08,599 --> 00:28:09,920
But when we order tests,

819
00:28:10,000 --> 00:28:11,200
we first need a clear direction

820
00:28:11,200 --> 00:28:12,039
and then screen possibilities one by one.

821
00:28:12,480 --> 00:28:14,279
That helps avoid

822
00:28:14,319 --> 00:28:15,759
unnecessary over-testing.

823
00:28:16,200 --> 00:28:16,920
It also takes

824
00:28:16,920 --> 00:28:17,920
cost into account.

825
00:28:18,200 --> 00:28:19,279
We save where we can

826
00:28:19,720 --> 00:28:20,839
and spend where we must.

827
00:28:26,000 --> 00:28:27,759
Fine. Do the tests.

828
00:28:28,799 --> 00:28:29,200
Let's see

829
00:28:29,240 --> 00:28:30,400
what you can find.

830
00:28:42,599 --> 00:28:43,160
Long Quan.

831
00:28:44,039 --> 00:28:44,440
Well...

832
00:28:44,799 --> 00:28:45,359
Jiaojiao.

833
00:28:46,079 --> 00:28:46,480
Ma'am,

834
00:28:46,480 --> 00:28:48,079
let me explain.

835
00:28:48,720 --> 00:28:49,880
Since we're already in the hospital,

836
00:28:49,960 --> 00:28:51,279
we should listen to the doctors.

837
00:28:51,440 --> 00:28:52,759
Whatever tests they recommend,

838
00:28:52,759 --> 00:28:54,000
we should do.

839
00:28:54,200 --> 00:28:55,000
They're being

840
00:28:55,039 --> 00:28:56,039
responsible for us, right?

841
00:28:56,400 --> 00:28:57,839
And Director Zhou

842
00:28:57,920 --> 00:28:59,279
is a very good person.

843
00:29:04,519 --> 00:29:06,160
How long have you had these symptoms?

844
00:29:07,599 --> 00:29:08,119
Mom.

845
00:29:08,839 --> 00:29:10,480
All right, stop it.

846
00:29:22,039 --> 00:29:23,599
To the three viewers in my livestream,

847
00:29:23,680 --> 00:29:24,799
keep tapping the like button.

848
00:29:24,880 --> 00:29:25,920
Don't stop.

849
00:29:26,279 --> 00:29:27,279
Let me show everyone

850
00:29:27,319 --> 00:29:29,039
the hospital I've stayed in for three days.

851
00:29:29,480 --> 00:29:30,440
The environment

852
00:29:30,440 --> 00:29:31,359
is actually pretty good.

853
00:29:32,839 --> 00:29:33,319
Look.

854
00:29:35,599 --> 00:29:36,119
Zhaobang.

855
00:29:36,400 --> 00:29:37,720
Why are you only coming now?

856
00:29:38,000 --> 00:29:39,119
Everyone, give me a moment.

857
00:29:39,559 --> 00:29:40,160
What are you doing?

858
00:29:40,400 --> 00:29:41,039
Livestreaming.

859
00:29:42,079 --> 00:29:42,799
What happened to this?

860
00:29:43,960 --> 00:29:45,200
A couple days ago,

861
00:29:45,720 --> 00:29:46,359
I was fixing some wiring

862
00:29:47,599 --> 00:29:48,799
and scraped it.

863
00:29:49,440 --> 00:29:50,559
The hospital has been asking for payment

864
00:29:50,559 --> 00:29:51,720
for days.

865
00:29:51,720 --> 00:29:52,480
Why did you wait so long to come?

866
00:29:54,519 --> 00:29:55,920
I meant to come yesterday,

867
00:29:56,039 --> 00:29:57,599
but the village official from your family village

868
00:29:57,640 --> 00:29:58,319
came to see me again

869
00:29:59,079 --> 00:29:59,920
Is it still about

870
00:29:59,920 --> 00:30:01,079
your land compensation?

871
00:30:01,240 --> 00:30:02,240
What did the official say?

872
00:30:02,799 --> 00:30:03,680
What else could he say?

873
00:30:03,839 --> 00:30:04,720
He made it very clear.

874
00:30:04,799 --> 00:30:05,559
You don't get a share.

875
00:30:05,680 --> 00:30:07,079
And you should stop going back to ask.

876
00:30:07,119 --> 00:30:08,039
Why?

877
00:30:08,079 --> 00:30:09,960
My household registration is still there.

878
00:30:10,880 --> 00:30:11,880
Which room are you staying in?

879
00:30:12,440 --> 00:30:13,359
I'm in this double room.

880
00:30:14,400 --> 00:30:15,039
Then go back and rest first.

881
00:30:15,079 --> 00:30:16,440
We'll talk about it later.

882
00:30:16,599 --> 00:30:18,480
All right.

883
00:30:18,519 --> 00:30:19,119
Let's go.

884
00:30:19,200 --> 00:30:20,519
Did your sisters Zhao'e and Ling'e get any?

885
00:30:20,559 --> 00:30:21,359
No.

886
00:30:21,440 --> 00:30:21,880
But I...

887
00:30:22,640 --> 00:30:23,119
Long Quan,

888
00:30:23,559 --> 00:30:24,359
let me introduce you.

889
00:30:24,359 --> 00:30:25,559
This is my husband, Zhaobang.

890
00:30:27,000 --> 00:30:27,640
Long Jiaojiao.

891
00:30:28,039 --> 00:30:28,960
Not bad, huh?

892
00:30:29,160 --> 00:30:30,160
Just because I married

893
00:30:30,160 --> 00:30:31,359
doesn't mean I'm dead.

894
00:30:31,400 --> 00:30:32,880
Why shouldn't I get a share?

895
00:30:34,480 --> 00:30:35,480
What kind of logic is that?

896
00:30:39,880 --> 00:30:42,200
The official looked into it.

897
00:30:43,119 --> 00:30:45,480
When our village handled

898
00:30:45,519 --> 00:30:46,759
homestead demolition and resettlement,

899
00:30:47,160 --> 00:30:48,920
daughters weren't counted

900
00:30:50,319 --> 00:30:51,720
because they would marry out eventually.

901
00:30:52,599 --> 00:30:53,480
I'm a son.

902
00:30:54,400 --> 00:30:55,279
Under the rules,

903
00:30:55,480 --> 00:30:57,000
I received homestead land

904
00:30:57,000 --> 00:30:57,920
for three people.

905
00:30:58,599 --> 00:30:59,960
That already includes

906
00:30:59,960 --> 00:31:01,400
my wife and child.

907
00:31:01,799 --> 00:31:03,839
If you claim another share

908
00:31:04,119 --> 00:31:05,319
from your birth family,

909
00:31:05,599 --> 00:31:06,680
you'd be getting double.

910
00:31:08,400 --> 00:31:09,160
That doesn't seem fair either.

911
00:31:09,160 --> 00:31:10,200
Is my name

912
00:31:12,039 --> 00:31:14,160
on your property deed?

913
00:31:14,240 --> 00:31:15,559
We weren't married

914
00:31:17,039 --> 00:31:17,960
when your family built the house.

915
00:31:17,960 --> 00:31:19,599
What's yours is yours.

916
00:31:20,200 --> 00:31:20,599
I want my own share.

917
00:31:20,599 --> 00:31:22,359
Why is it that

918
00:31:22,400 --> 00:31:23,599
sons get money and land,

919
00:31:23,960 --> 00:31:24,640
but daughters don't count as people?

920
00:31:24,960 --> 00:31:25,799
I don't care.

921
00:31:29,000 --> 00:31:31,119
I'm going back again.

922
00:31:34,279 --> 00:31:35,880
Why won't you listen?

923
00:31:35,920 --> 00:31:37,200
Everyone around your parents' home

924
00:31:38,000 --> 00:31:39,519
is cursing you,

925
00:31:40,160 --> 00:31:41,680
calling you shameless.

926
00:31:41,680 --> 00:31:42,720
They say a married daughter

927
00:31:42,720 --> 00:31:45,039
is water poured away.

928
00:31:45,799 --> 00:31:47,440
Must you fight the whole village?

929
00:31:47,759 --> 00:31:49,160
Even your parents told you to stop.

930
00:31:49,200 --> 00:31:49,960
Otherwise they can't face anyone there.

931
00:31:50,119 --> 00:31:50,920
Do you understand?

932
00:31:52,480 --> 00:31:53,759
That official too...

933
00:31:54,119 --> 00:31:55,640
This is my business. He should talk to me.

934
00:31:55,640 --> 00:31:56,680
Why did he go to you?

935
00:31:56,799 --> 00:31:58,480
He asked me to control you.

936
00:31:58,480 --> 00:31:59,880
Can you act sensibly for once?

937
00:32:01,200 --> 00:32:01,799
Why are you arguing?

938
00:32:01,839 --> 00:32:02,480
Dr. Ye.

939
00:32:04,079 --> 00:32:05,000
This is a hospital.

940
00:32:09,119 --> 00:32:10,279
Are you Zhang Diao'e's family?

941
00:32:12,920 --> 00:32:13,759
You finally came.

942
00:32:14,319 --> 00:32:15,160
Have you paid the deposit?

943
00:32:16,000 --> 00:32:17,359
Not yet. I was just about to.

944
00:32:17,799 --> 00:32:18,319
Hurry.

945
00:32:20,160 --> 00:32:21,920
And couldn't you have changed clothes?

946
00:32:23,160 --> 00:32:24,480
Here are the clothes you asked for.

947
00:32:25,960 --> 00:32:27,480
Look at him.

948
00:32:28,480 --> 00:32:29,240
My husband.

949
00:32:29,680 --> 00:32:30,200
Handsome, right?

950
00:32:35,759 --> 00:32:36,640
Does any of this make sense?

951
00:32:36,920 --> 00:32:38,119
Quan, you heard him.

952
00:32:38,279 --> 00:32:40,000
Tell me, are they being reasonable?

953
00:32:41,160 --> 00:32:43,000
My husband looks all right, right?

954
00:32:45,039 --> 00:32:46,079
Still acting like this.

955
00:32:54,079 --> 00:32:54,880
Try the payment again.

956
00:33:05,039 --> 00:33:05,680
Still not working.

957
00:33:06,000 --> 00:33:06,720
The charge failed.

958
00:33:07,519 --> 00:33:08,519
Check whether

959
00:33:08,599 --> 00:33:09,839
there's enough money in the account.

960
00:33:11,400 --> 00:33:12,039
Hey, everyone.

961
00:33:12,519 --> 00:33:14,480
Like, follow, and share.

962
00:33:15,000 --> 00:33:16,960
Tap all three buttons.

963
00:33:17,599 --> 00:33:19,559
Xiao'e may be injured, but she's strong.

964
00:33:22,400 --> 00:33:23,240
Love you all.

965
00:33:25,759 --> 00:33:26,359
The doctor is here.

966
00:33:26,359 --> 00:33:27,200
Zhang Diao'e,

967
00:33:27,680 --> 00:33:28,960
can't you rest for a while?

968
00:33:28,960 --> 00:33:29,599
See you later.

969
00:33:30,440 --> 00:33:31,720
Now you're dancing too?

970
00:33:31,799 --> 00:33:32,599
Quan,

971
00:33:32,640 --> 00:33:33,240
how are you

972
00:33:33,279 --> 00:33:34,680
so good at this?

973
00:33:35,279 --> 00:33:36,200
Jiaojiao.

974
00:33:36,440 --> 00:33:37,200
Jiaojiao. Jiaojiao.

975
00:33:37,440 --> 00:33:38,480
Just show me a couple of moves.

976
00:33:38,480 --> 00:33:39,079
Look.

977
00:33:39,160 --> 00:33:41,240
My livestream numbers keep rising.

978
00:33:41,680 --> 00:33:42,400
Dr. Ye,

979
00:33:42,640 --> 00:33:43,799
did you know

980
00:33:43,839 --> 00:33:45,039
we were classmates?

981
00:33:45,279 --> 00:33:47,880
Back then, we even held hands

982
00:33:47,920 --> 00:33:48,359
when we went to the bathroom.

983
00:33:49,720 --> 00:33:50,359
Not really.

984
00:33:50,400 --> 00:33:52,119
Later, she studied hard,

985
00:33:52,160 --> 00:33:53,720
got into a top high school,

986
00:33:53,720 --> 00:33:55,279
then a top university.

987
00:33:55,319 --> 00:33:56,880
I was never academic.

988
00:33:57,279 --> 00:33:58,039
I left after middle school

989
00:33:58,079 --> 00:33:59,640
and learned tailoring.

990
00:33:59,920 --> 00:34:01,880
All right. Get some rest.

991
00:34:02,400 --> 00:34:03,640
And don't disturb other patients.

992
00:34:04,000 --> 00:34:05,720
We have endless things to talk about.

993
00:34:05,839 --> 00:34:07,240
She's only shy

994
00:34:07,240 --> 00:34:08,039
because she just saw me again.

995
00:34:08,119 --> 00:34:08,639
Right, Quan?

996
00:34:08,880 --> 00:34:09,800
Zhang Diao'e.

997
00:34:10,880 --> 00:34:11,440
You're back.

998
00:34:17,639 --> 00:34:18,119
What's wrong?

999
00:34:21,719 --> 00:34:22,440
Where's your money?

1000
00:34:22,920 --> 00:34:23,960
I remember there were several thousand in there.

1001
00:34:23,960 --> 00:34:25,000
How is there only thirty-some yuan left?

1002
00:34:25,840 --> 00:34:27,079
You took this card.

1003
00:34:27,159 --> 00:34:28,639
There's no money left in it.

1004
00:34:29,360 --> 00:34:30,280
I used it to enroll in

1005
00:34:30,360 --> 00:34:31,840
an elite livestream coaching course.

1006
00:34:32,199 --> 00:34:33,679
What? What kind of course?

1007
00:34:33,760 --> 00:34:34,679
You learn

1008
00:34:34,679 --> 00:34:36,639
how to livestream with a mentor.

1009
00:34:36,719 --> 00:34:37,840
One of our senior students

1010
00:34:38,039 --> 00:34:39,559
bought a luxury car

1011
00:34:39,760 --> 00:34:41,039
in cash for hundreds of thousands

1012
00:34:41,360 --> 00:34:42,599
and earns over a million a year.

1013
00:34:45,800 --> 00:34:46,480
So what?

1014
00:34:50,639 --> 00:34:52,239
Are you

1015
00:34:52,280 --> 00:34:53,239
out of your mind too?

1016
00:34:53,239 --> 00:34:55,079
Would something that good ever fall to you?

1017
00:34:55,079 --> 00:34:55,840
A million a year?

1018
00:34:56,119 --> 00:34:57,760
I'm not even afraid to say it.

1019
00:34:57,880 --> 00:34:58,400
Last year,

1020
00:34:58,480 --> 00:34:59,519
you got scammed selling products online.

1021
00:35:00,039 --> 00:35:01,440
You filled the whole house

1022
00:35:01,559 --> 00:35:02,519
with facial masks.

1023
00:35:02,559 --> 00:35:03,280
In the end,

1024
00:35:03,280 --> 00:35:04,079
you couldn't even give them away.

1025
00:35:04,159 --> 00:35:04,440
I...

1026
00:35:04,679 --> 00:35:06,320
And before that, you did fake-order schemes.

1027
00:35:06,800 --> 00:35:08,360
I won't even mention the money you lost.

1028
00:35:08,480 --> 00:35:09,679
You nearly got arrested.

1029
00:35:09,679 --> 00:35:10,440
Am I wrong?

1030
00:35:10,519 --> 00:35:11,920
Why can't you

1031
00:35:11,920 --> 00:35:13,079
learn from your mistakes?

1032
00:35:13,840 --> 00:35:14,800
This time is different.

1033
00:35:14,800 --> 00:35:15,360
How is it different?

1034
00:35:15,440 --> 00:35:16,159
Tell me how.

1035
00:35:16,239 --> 00:35:17,679
Lots of senior members in our group

1036
00:35:17,719 --> 00:35:19,280
have already made money.

1037
00:35:19,599 --> 00:35:20,360
Enough.

1038
00:35:20,519 --> 00:35:21,800
When I get the money back,

1039
00:35:21,800 --> 00:35:22,719
let's see what you say then.

1040
00:35:23,000 --> 00:35:24,039
You...

1041
00:35:25,360 --> 00:35:26,239
You want to hit me?

1042
00:35:29,440 --> 00:35:30,360
Family member, please be careful.

1043
00:35:31,039 --> 00:35:32,480
The patient must not get agitated.

1044
00:35:35,320 --> 00:35:36,880
It's obviously a scam.

1045
00:35:37,239 --> 00:35:39,320
The police anti-fraud campaigns warned about this.

1046
00:35:39,679 --> 00:35:41,400
How can you still believe it?

1047
00:35:41,440 --> 00:35:42,920
Ma'am, this really is different.

1048
00:35:43,079 --> 00:35:43,920
Everyone in our group

1049
00:35:43,920 --> 00:35:45,039
knows one another.

1050
00:35:45,119 --> 00:35:46,320
That senior woman I mentioned

1051
00:35:46,599 --> 00:35:47,360
even posted

1052
00:35:47,480 --> 00:35:48,880
a video of herself picking up her new car

1053
00:35:48,880 --> 00:35:50,199
in the group.

1054
00:35:50,400 --> 00:35:52,239
She sent sales records,

1055
00:35:52,239 --> 00:35:53,360
bank statements,

1056
00:35:53,400 --> 00:35:54,599
all kinds of proof.

1057
00:35:54,880 --> 00:35:56,559
She couldn't fake all that.

1058
00:36:08,840 --> 00:36:10,159
If she had a real way to make money,

1059
00:36:10,159 --> 00:36:11,440
why would she tell you?

1060
00:36:12,480 --> 00:36:13,920
You're a grown woman.

1061
00:36:14,400 --> 00:36:16,079
Stop dreaming about money falling from the sky.

1062
00:36:16,280 --> 00:36:17,639
The only thing falling is a trap.

1063
00:36:18,360 --> 00:36:19,559
Don't look down on me.

1064
00:36:20,960 --> 00:36:21,719
I don't care.

1065
00:36:22,519 --> 00:36:23,840
I'm going to work hard

1066
00:36:23,840 --> 00:36:24,679
and learn properly.

1067
00:36:25,320 --> 00:36:26,840
Once my livestream numbers soar,

1068
00:36:26,840 --> 00:36:27,559
I'll monetize it.

1069
00:36:27,639 --> 00:36:29,519
I'll put real cash in front of you

1070
00:36:29,719 --> 00:36:30,840
and see what you say then.

1071
00:36:31,159 --> 00:36:32,320
Our slogan is:

1072
00:36:32,559 --> 00:36:33,760
"We give you the first step

1073
00:36:34,079 --> 00:36:35,840
toward the peak of your life."

1074
00:36:37,760 --> 00:36:39,039
Zhang Diao'e's husband called the police.

1075
00:36:39,559 --> 00:36:40,840
They said it was

1076
00:36:41,159 --> 00:36:42,199
a scam specifically targeting

1077
00:36:42,239 --> 00:36:43,280
stay-at-home mothers

1078
00:36:44,000 --> 00:36:46,559
A what kind of scam?

1079
00:36:46,719 --> 00:36:47,679
It's scammer slang.

1080
00:36:48,039 --> 00:36:49,719
They call victims "birds."

1081
00:36:50,519 --> 00:36:51,480
I've seen exposés

1082
00:36:51,480 --> 00:36:53,000
about similar cases.

1083
00:36:53,239 --> 00:36:54,199
These mothers

1084
00:36:54,239 --> 00:36:55,559
are tied down at home

1085
00:36:55,599 --> 00:36:56,360
by children and housework.

1086
00:36:56,360 --> 00:36:57,159
They're described

1087
00:36:57,159 --> 00:36:58,639
as birds trapped in cages.

1088
00:36:59,440 --> 00:37:00,440
They have no income

1089
00:37:00,440 --> 00:37:01,840
and want to help with household expenses.

1090
00:37:03,480 --> 00:37:04,320
That's vile.

1091
00:37:04,679 --> 00:37:06,639
They specifically target mothers.

1092
00:37:07,559 --> 00:37:09,159
Their schedules aren't flexible,

1093
00:37:09,320 --> 00:37:11,199
and some are disconnected from society.

1094
00:37:11,239 --> 00:37:12,280
Even if they want to return to work,

1095
00:37:12,280 --> 00:37:13,079
they can't immediately

1096
00:37:13,079 --> 00:37:14,039
find a job.

1097
00:37:14,360 --> 00:37:15,519
These scammers exploit

1098
00:37:15,519 --> 00:37:16,280
exactly those vulnerabilities.

1099
00:37:16,679 --> 00:37:18,000
My best friend encountered one too.

1100
00:37:18,599 --> 00:37:19,760
She almost fell for it.

1101
00:37:20,000 --> 00:37:21,199
They told her

1102
00:37:21,320 --> 00:37:22,960
the entry barrier was low and hours flexible.

1103
00:37:23,239 --> 00:37:25,199
At first,

1104
00:37:25,199 --> 00:37:25,760
she really

1105
00:37:26,159 --> 00:37:26,800
made some money.

1106
00:37:26,960 --> 00:37:28,199
They let her taste a little success.

1107
00:37:28,840 --> 00:37:29,519
But later,

1108
00:37:29,840 --> 00:37:31,280
they tricked her into paying

1109
00:37:31,519 --> 00:37:33,639
training fees, order-taking fees,

1110
00:37:34,079 --> 00:37:34,840
and deposits for selling products.

1111
00:37:35,159 --> 00:37:35,760
Things like that.

1112
00:37:36,239 --> 00:37:37,599
Now they're organized teams.

1113
00:37:38,000 --> 00:37:39,440
They have detailed scripts and clear roles.

1114
00:37:39,800 --> 00:37:40,639
They even hire actors

1115
00:37:40,760 --> 00:37:41,760
and use acquaintances as shills.

1116
00:37:42,159 --> 00:37:43,519
That's what happened to Zhang Diao'e.

1117
00:37:43,760 --> 00:37:45,639
She was desperate for work and money.

1118
00:37:46,039 --> 00:37:46,920
More importantly,

1119
00:37:47,159 --> 00:37:48,679
she wanted to prove her own value.

1120
00:37:49,000 --> 00:37:50,440
Depending on someone else for money

1121
00:37:50,440 --> 00:37:51,199
doesn't feel good either.

1122
00:37:51,440 --> 00:37:54,320
You rotten scammer! Liar!

1123
00:37:54,559 --> 00:37:56,360
Why did you scam me?

1124
00:37:56,360 --> 00:37:57,159
You...

1125
00:37:57,360 --> 00:37:58,199
You heartless bastard!

1126
00:37:58,199 --> 00:37:58,920
Stop wailing.

1127
00:37:59,000 --> 00:37:59,480
Look at the state I'm in.

1128
00:37:59,480 --> 00:38:00,400
Can you stop yelling?

1129
00:38:00,400 --> 00:38:02,519
Why did they have to scam me?

1130
00:38:02,519 --> 00:38:03,639
My head is buzzing.

1131
00:38:03,639 --> 00:38:04,400
Stop yelling.

1132
00:38:04,559 --> 00:38:05,400
I'm furious.

1133
00:38:07,239 --> 00:38:08,320
I only wanted

1134
00:38:08,320 --> 00:38:10,239
to help with household expenses.

1135
00:38:11,199 --> 00:38:13,400
You always say I have two hands and feet

1136
00:38:13,519 --> 00:38:15,599
but leave you to support the family alone.

1137
00:38:15,800 --> 00:38:17,639
And then you go and throw money away.

1138
00:38:18,000 --> 00:38:18,480
Honestly,

1139
00:38:18,559 --> 00:38:20,480
I've had enough.

1140
00:38:21,280 --> 00:38:23,400
Several thousand yuan!

1141
00:38:23,480 --> 00:38:25,760
How long will it take me to earn that back?

1142
00:38:26,480 --> 00:38:27,719
Those scammers!

1143
00:38:27,719 --> 00:38:28,519
Zhang Diao'e,

1144
00:38:30,239 --> 00:38:31,000
and family member,

1145
00:38:31,599 --> 00:38:32,599
the director wants to speak with you.

1146
00:38:33,079 --> 00:38:33,599
Hurry.

1147
00:38:34,119 --> 00:38:34,639
We know.

1148
00:38:36,719 --> 00:38:37,360
Zhaobang,

1149
00:38:38,280 --> 00:38:40,159
I really know I was wrong this time.

1150
00:38:40,320 --> 00:38:42,039
I'll never do it again.

1151
00:38:44,199 --> 00:38:44,920
All right, enough.

1152
00:38:45,079 --> 00:38:45,679
Let's go.

1153
00:38:47,400 --> 00:38:48,440
Here we go again.

1154
00:38:48,559 --> 00:38:49,639
All thunder and no rain.

1155
00:38:49,960 --> 00:38:51,360
It's just one month's work gone.

1156
00:38:51,440 --> 00:38:52,360
It's not the end of the world.

1157
00:38:52,440 --> 00:38:53,320
Get down. Hurry.

1158
00:38:53,440 --> 00:38:54,199
No, you...

1159
00:38:57,440 --> 00:38:58,039
I'm saying

1160
00:38:58,559 --> 00:38:59,960
your husband isn't bad.

1161
00:39:00,480 --> 00:39:01,960
Even now, he's still looking after you.

1162
00:39:02,480 --> 00:39:03,599
When something happens,

1163
00:39:03,880 --> 00:39:05,320
talk it over with him.

1164
00:39:05,320 --> 00:39:06,039
Understand?

1165
00:39:13,159 --> 00:39:13,760
Jiaojiao,

1166
00:39:14,679 --> 00:39:15,599
that person...

1167
00:39:15,960 --> 00:39:17,039
why hasn't he come yet?

1168
00:39:18,000 --> 00:39:19,199
He said he's been busy lately.

1169
00:39:19,239 --> 00:39:20,039
He just called.

1170
00:39:21,039 --> 00:39:22,760
You've been in the hospital for days.

1171
00:39:22,800 --> 00:39:23,360
No matter how busy he is,

1172
00:39:23,639 --> 00:39:25,159
he should still come see you.

1173
00:39:26,719 --> 00:39:27,920
Brother Xu asked me to transfer this to you.

1174
00:39:28,000 --> 00:39:29,280
He said you've worked hard lately.

1175
00:39:34,440 --> 00:39:35,559
I'm not tired.

1176
00:39:36,719 --> 00:39:37,440
That's a lot.

1177
00:39:40,760 --> 00:39:41,880
What does your husband

1178
00:39:43,480 --> 00:39:44,320
do?

1179
00:39:44,760 --> 00:39:46,039
He's the boss of Jiaojiao's company.

1180
00:39:46,440 --> 00:39:47,320
They're not married yet.

1181
00:39:47,719 --> 00:39:49,119
It's only a matter of time.

1182
00:39:49,159 --> 00:39:50,039
He's generous.

1183
00:39:50,599 --> 00:39:51,679
He must be paying

1184
00:39:51,840 --> 00:39:52,840
all her hospital bills too.

1185
00:39:53,880 --> 00:39:54,679
He's not my boss.

1186
00:39:55,519 --> 00:39:56,519
He's my business partner.

1187
00:39:57,679 --> 00:39:58,960
Every cent I spend

1188
00:39:58,960 --> 00:40:00,039
is money I earned myself.

1189
00:40:00,719 --> 00:40:01,239
Impressive.

1190
00:40:01,760 --> 00:40:02,599
A strong career woman.

1191
00:40:02,880 --> 00:40:03,559
I'm jealous.

1192
00:40:03,679 --> 00:40:05,000
Go on.

1193
00:40:10,440 --> 00:40:11,400
I'm not tired.

1194
00:40:22,480 --> 00:40:23,000
Based on

1195
00:40:23,000 --> 00:40:23,519
the contrast-enhanced CT

1196
00:40:23,559 --> 00:40:24,360
results,

1197
00:40:24,480 --> 00:40:25,400
you have confirmed

1198
00:40:25,440 --> 00:40:26,880
multiple pulmonary arteriovenous malformations

1199
00:40:27,199 --> 00:40:27,960
They definitely require

1200
00:40:27,960 --> 00:40:28,760
immediate intervention.

1201
00:40:29,239 --> 00:40:30,880
One option is transcatheter embolization,

1202
00:40:31,119 --> 00:40:31,760
which blocks

1203
00:40:31,760 --> 00:40:33,280
the abnormal vessels.

1204
00:40:34,039 --> 00:40:35,320
Then I can get pregnant

1205
00:40:35,320 --> 00:40:36,199
and have a baby, right?

1206
00:40:38,360 --> 00:40:39,679
Your condition is complicated.

1207
00:40:40,079 --> 00:40:40,960
One procedure

1208
00:40:40,960 --> 00:40:41,639
may not be enough.

1209
00:40:41,639 --> 00:40:42,440
You may need a second.

1210
00:40:42,920 --> 00:40:44,360
Only after your health is stable

1211
00:40:44,800 --> 00:40:46,119
can you consider pregnancy.

1212
00:40:49,320 --> 00:40:50,519
Another option

1213
00:40:50,880 --> 00:40:52,320
is thoracoscopic surgery.

1214
00:40:52,920 --> 00:40:53,880
We'd make a small incision

1215
00:40:53,920 --> 00:40:54,920
between your ribs,

1216
00:40:55,159 --> 00:40:56,079
then remove

1217
00:40:56,119 --> 00:40:57,800
the diseased part of the lung.

1218
00:41:05,599 --> 00:41:06,119
Look.

1219
00:41:08,239 --> 00:41:09,679
Imagine this is your lung

1220
00:41:09,800 --> 00:41:10,880
and it's a wall.

1221
00:41:11,800 --> 00:41:12,840
But the wall

1222
00:41:12,840 --> 00:41:14,199
has developed mouse holes.

1223
00:41:15,239 --> 00:41:16,400
The interventional approach

1224
00:41:16,599 --> 00:41:17,280
blocks the holes

1225
00:41:17,280 --> 00:41:18,599
one by one.

1226
00:41:18,960 --> 00:41:20,239
But if any are missed,

1227
00:41:20,639 --> 00:41:21,559
the mice and their offspring

1228
00:41:21,559 --> 00:41:22,639
can keep causing trouble.

1229
00:41:23,239 --> 00:41:24,559
With surgery,

1230
00:41:25,960 --> 00:41:27,119
we simply tear down that part of the wall,

1231
00:41:27,519 --> 00:41:28,880
eliminating the problem at its root.

1232
00:41:30,559 --> 00:41:32,159
So once the wall is removed,

1233
00:41:32,159 --> 00:41:33,360
I can get pregnant?

1234
00:41:34,400 --> 00:41:34,840
No.

1235
00:41:36,119 --> 00:41:37,760
Did you understand

1236
00:41:37,760 --> 00:41:38,599
anything we just said?

1237
00:41:39,440 --> 00:41:41,199
This is not about pregnancy right now.

1238
00:41:41,360 --> 00:41:42,800
This is about your life.

1239
00:41:43,920 --> 00:41:44,360
I...

1240
00:41:44,639 --> 00:41:45,800
Director Lin is right.

1241
00:41:46,239 --> 00:41:47,559
Whether it's thoracoscopic surgery

1242
00:41:47,599 --> 00:41:48,679
or an interventional procedure,

1243
00:41:49,079 --> 00:41:50,239
the goal is the same:

1244
00:41:50,519 --> 00:41:51,639
to cure your condition.

1245
00:41:51,760 --> 00:41:52,840
Only when you're healthy

1246
00:41:53,119 --> 00:41:54,559
can you consider pregnancy.

1247
00:41:54,719 --> 00:41:55,519
But

1248
00:41:55,800 --> 00:41:57,159
the obstetrician said

1249
00:41:57,199 --> 00:41:57,719
one of my test results

1250
00:41:57,800 --> 00:41:59,239
wasn't very good.

1251
00:41:59,519 --> 00:42:00,599
Right?

1252
00:42:01,559 --> 00:42:03,519
She said I have to get pregnant soon

1253
00:42:03,519 --> 00:42:05,119
or I might not be able to.

1254
00:42:06,360 --> 00:42:08,000
Say something.

1255
00:42:08,159 --> 00:42:09,360
What do you want me to say?

1256
00:42:09,400 --> 00:42:11,039
About getting pregnant.

1257
00:42:11,800 --> 00:42:13,159
I...

1258
00:42:16,679 --> 00:42:17,440
It's up to her.

1259
00:42:18,760 --> 00:42:20,440
She's determined to have a son.

1260
00:42:21,719 --> 00:42:23,440
I'm not forcing her.

1261
00:42:24,000 --> 00:42:24,719
I'm having a son

1262
00:42:24,719 --> 00:42:26,440
for you, aren't I?

1263
00:42:27,760 --> 00:42:28,280
Director Zhou,

1264
00:42:28,360 --> 00:42:30,079
you're in charge. I trust you.

1265
00:42:30,639 --> 00:42:31,480
Please.

1266
00:42:31,599 --> 00:42:32,719
Once you tear down this wall,

1267
00:42:32,719 --> 00:42:34,320
I have to have a baby this year.

1268
00:42:35,599 --> 00:42:36,280
Zhang Diao'e,

1269
00:42:37,519 --> 00:42:38,920
put pregnancy aside for now.

1270
00:42:39,480 --> 00:42:40,440
The most important thing

1271
00:42:40,480 --> 00:42:41,719
is treating your illness.

1272
00:42:44,360 --> 00:42:45,840
You two should discuss it carefully.

1273
00:42:49,599 --> 00:42:51,519
How did I end up with this disease?

1274
00:42:51,519 --> 00:42:52,239
What terrible luck.
